    - Russian (ru.po) by Yuri Kozlov
    - Turkish (tr.po) by Recai Oktaş
    - Ukrainian (uk.po) by Eugeniy Meshcheryakov
    - Simplified Chinese (zh_CN.po) by Carlos Z.F. Liu

 -- Joey Hess <joeyh@debian.org>  Mon, 30 Aug 2004 12:13:24 -0400

